    <Folder>
      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The US military has carried out strikes on Iranian targets in the Strait of Hormuz, including Qesham Port and Bandar Abbas. The U.S. claims these were self-defense responses to Iranian attacks, but Iran maintains they were provocative. This incident marks a sharp escalation since a truce was signed earlier this month.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
